name: plain text
text: Guests must carry Portable Mobile Chargers and Power Banks in their hand baggage as they are not allowed in checked-in baggage for safety reasons. It is advised to pack fragile items securely to prevent damage, as the airline will not be held responsible for any damage.

name: plain text
text: Two (2) check-in bags are included for Xpress Biz Fares and on all international flights One (1) check-in bag is included for all other fares on domestic flights. Extra charges are levied for any additional pieces of baggage. Pre-book up to 40 kg excess baggage / extra piece(s) at lower than airport prices. Guests travelling on the same PNR, can combine baggage allowances. Each bag should weigh no more than 32 kg.

name: plain text
text: for international flights, the first 20 kg costs INR 2oo0 at the airport. Also, remember that if. your booking is in non-INR currency, the baggage price might vary at the airport..

name: plain text
text: When packing your bags, please keep in mind the items that are prohibited from being carried and the regulations on the carriage of liquids, aerosols and gels.
